{"tid":699170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美朝官員午餐食揚州炒飯 甜品食Häagen-Dazs","createTime":"2018-06-12T09:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T10:40:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a967c239ffd7f02e356716d78784892b0e635711","tid":699170,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/6/1528776876_bv-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F6%2F1528776876_bv-1280w.jpg&h=dee37a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被稱為「世紀談判」的美朝峰會於新加坡聖淘沙嘉佩樂酒店召開。美國總統特朗普與北韓領袖金正恩完成大約45分鐘的單對單會談後，雙方官員再加入進行約90分鐘的雙邊會談，其後進行工作午餐。<br />\n據當地傳媒報道，今次美朝官員的工作午餐，包括頭盤有鮮蝦、牛油果沙律；主菜是牛肋排、大邱燉菜及揚州炒飯等，甜品是H&auml;agen-Dazs雪糕。<br />\n預料傍晚特朗普會於聖淘沙召開記者會。特朗普晚上會從巴耶利峇空軍基地離開新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/6/1528778286_8h-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F6%2F1528778286_8h-1280w.jpg&h=08ce7e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【特金會】美朝官員午餐食揚州炒飯-甜品食h&auml;agen-dazs-129698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E3%80%90%E7%89%B9%E9%87%91%E6%9C%83%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E6%9C%9D%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E5%8D%88%E9%A4%90%E9%A3%9F%E6%8F%9A%E5%B7%9E%E7%82%92%E9%A3%AF-%E7%94%9C%E5%93%81%E9%A3%9Fh%C3%A4agen-dazs-129698&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7482ba90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【特金會】美朝官員午餐食揚州炒飯-甜品食h&auml;agen-dazs-129698</a>"},{"pid":"14ec3d97257680b383caf86ec862c09527f0be25","tid":699170,"uid":111253,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:53:16.000Z","msg":"哈根大師呢下廣告堅料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275d8521df71937bbd5ad0687e40c637ffb1b531","tid":699170,"uid":132587,"like":0,"disl